  section.guides#voice
    .section-content
      h2 Voice
      p The essence of who we are comes from our purpose to deliver happiness to our clients.  But that’s not just lip service: it’s something we live by here at Legwork.  Employees lend a hand when needed.  If someone is feeling overwhelmed, others step in and help.  Our voice as a company should exemplify the intrinsic nature of how we treat others.  This means writing for Legwork should be clear, friendly, and straightforward.  We want to be helpful, but not overbearing, expert, yet modest.  Above all, we aim to treat people with respect and cultivate happiness.
  section.guides#the-logo
