      h2 Color Palette
      p Our colors help define value and strengthen our purpose to deliver happiness both inside and outside of the company. Designs created for our brand should be inviting, yet professional. Tints of colors are permitted as long as the integrity of the color is maintained. Deep Sea should be treated as our brand’s black.
      .subsection.color-subsection
